graph TD
    %% Development Branch Structure
    Dev[Development<br/>Local NixOS]
    Feature[Feature Branch<br/>claude/feature-name]
    Main[Main Branch<br/>Production Ready]
    
    %% Single-User Development
    DevDB[(Local PostgreSQL<br/>sinex_dev)]
    DevCollector[UnifiedCollector<br/>Development Config]
    DevWorker[Local Workers<br/>Parallelism: 1-2]
    
    %% Development Flow
    Dev --> |nix develop| DevShell[Development Shell]
    DevShell --> |just migrate| DevDB
    DevShell --> |cargo run collector| DevCollector
    DevShell --> |cargo run worker| DevWorker
    DevShell --> |./cli/exo.py| DevCLI[Development CLI]
    
    %% Testing Phases
    DevCollector --> UnitTests[Unit Tests<br/>~85% Coverage]
    DevWorker --> IntegrationTests[Integration Tests<br/>~75% Coverage]
    DevCLI --> SystemTests[System Tests<br/>~65% Coverage]
    
    %% Branch Promotion
    UnitTests --> |All Pass| Feature
    IntegrationTests --> |All Pass| Feature
    SystemTests --> |All Pass| Feature
    
    Feature --> |PR Review| CI[GitHub Actions CI]
    CI --> |Tests + Checks| Main
    
    %% Production Deployment Models
    Main --> SingleUser[Single-User Production]
    Main --> MultiUser[Multi-User + Agents]
    
    %% Single-User Production
    SingleUser --> ProdNix[NixOS Configuration]
    ProdNix --> ProdDB[(PostgreSQL<br/>Production DB)]
    ProdNix --> ProdCollector[UnifiedCollector<br/>Production Config]
    ProdNix --> ProdWorker[Production Workers<br/>Parallelism: 4-8]
    ProdNix --> ProdMetrics[Prometheus Metrics]
    
    %% Multi-User + Agents Architecture
    MultiUser --> CentralDB[(Central Database<br/>Multi-Tenant)]
    MultiUser --> UserCollectors[User-Specific Collectors]
    MultiUser --> CentralWorkers[Centralized Workers<br/>High Parallelism]
    
    %% User Collectors
    UserCollectors --> Alice[Alice's Collector<br/>Partition: alice]
    UserCollectors --> Bob[Bob's Collector<br/>Partition: bob]
    UserCollectors --> Charlie[Charlie's Collector<br/>Partition: charlie]
    
    %% Centralized Processing
    Alice --> CentralDB
    Bob --> CentralDB
    Charlie --> CentralDB
    CentralDB --> CentralWorkers
    CentralWorkers --> |Process All Partitions| Analytics[Cross-User Analytics]
    
    %% Monitoring & Operations
    ProdMetrics --> Grafana[Grafana Dashboards]
    CentralWorkers --> ClusterMetrics[Cluster Metrics]
    ClusterMetrics --> AlertManager[Alert Manager]
    
    %% Configuration Management
    ProdNix --> |services.sinex| NixConfig[Declarative Config]
    NixConfig --> Secrets[agenix Secrets]
    NixConfig --> SystemD[SystemD Services]
    
    %% Service Dependencies
    SystemD --> CollectorService[sinex-unified-collector.service]
    SystemD --> RouterService[sinex-router.service] 
    SystemD --> WorkerService[sinex-promo-worker.service]
    SystemD --> MetricsService[sinex-metrics.service]
    
    %% Git Flow Integration
    Feature --> |Commit| GitCommit[Git Commit<br/>Co-authored-by: Claude]
    GitCommit --> |Push| PR[Pull Request]
    PR --> |Merge| Main
    
    %% Release Process
    Main --> |Tag| Release[Release Tag<br/>v0.x.x]
    Release --> |Nix Build| Artifacts[Build Artifacts]
    Artifacts --> |Cachix| Cache[Binary Cache]
    Cache --> |Deploy| Production[Production Systems]
    
    %% Styling
    classDef dev fill:#e3f2fd
    classDef test fill:#f1f8e9
    classDef prod fill:#fff3e0
    classDef multi fill:#fce4ec
    classDef infra fill:#f3e5f5
    
    class Dev,DevShell,DevDB,DevCollector,DevWorker,DevCLI dev
    class UnitTests,IntegrationTests,SystemTests,CI test
    class SingleUser,ProdNix,ProdDB,ProdCollector,ProdWorker,ProdMetrics prod
    class MultiUser,CentralDB,UserCollectors,CentralWorkers,Alice,Bob,Charlie,Analytics multi
    class NixConfig,Secrets,SystemD,CollectorService,RouterService,WorkerService,MetricsService infra